name: Mirtazapine - NeonFlash 2/5 (Ghost Series collection)
description: Mirtazapine ghost series, vertical recordings in original colors, circa 2011. Created with self-built, modular, 3D generative video performance tool (built in Quartz Composer) . This generative tool no longer functions due to antiquated technology, all that remains is a handful of archival recordings; Ghost Series collection.
